3711e9e1d875"],

Cell["\<\
Now we will check our work. I have graphed the composition of the functions. \
Using the range of x values you found in 1(b), is the composition of the \
functions within 1/2 of 0 at x=2 for that range?\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.829738619177335*^9, 3.829738711065216*^9}, {
