d4a523ad65c8"],

Cell["\<\
More problems that are good practice for Problem 6 on the exam are all parts \
of Spivak Problem 3 of Spivak Chapter 5.\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.8297400078035603`*^9, 3.8297400324646177`*^9}, {
  3.829740091165308*^9, 3.829740098274469*^9}, {3.829740201144607*^9, 
