   3.829740912381254*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"2796e47d-5e70-4d0d-8554-\
954183047443"],

Cell["\<\
Thursday\[CloseCurlyQuote]s reading is to finish Chapter 6 (before the break \
you did to p. 115). The remaining two pages of the chapter are dense. You \
should try to prove the following two things before class. \
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.8284474725875397`*^9, 3.828447589824294*^9}, {
  3.828447670769052*^9, 3.82844769501711*^9}, {3.828447786409136*^9, 
  3.828447884611442*^9}, {3.828447919296382*^9, 3.828447993017722*^9}, {
  3.8284480339297037`*^9, 3.8284480387951593`*^9}, {3.8284481139503307`*^9, 
  3.828448231558095*^9}, {3.8297402766946383`*^9, 3.829740292157325*^9}, {
  3.829740323634078*^9, 3.82974034027992*^9}, {3.829740506812354*^9, 
  3.8297406077798777`*^9}, {3.8297406390488663`*^9, 
  3.829740658808031*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"446b700a-c4f7-48cc-b746-\
b353988cfe18"],

Cell[CellGroupData[{

Cell["\<\
(a) For in-class on Thursday, a proof related to Problem 7 on the exam\
\>", "Subsection",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.8297390093669977`*^9, 3.829739030122375*^9}, {
  3.829739483355031*^9, 3.829739484073804*^9}, {3.829739875335593*^9, 
  3.829739876628518*^9}, {3.82974064788583*^9, 3.8297406755487843`*^9}, {
  3.829741280173719*^9, 
  3.82974129045683*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"0b971a02-f9ee-4ff3-ac31-\
17412b8a5cdf"],

Cell[TextData[{
 "In problem 7, I tried for the easiest proof involving limits that I could \
come up with. The ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   RowBox[{"\[Delta]", "'"}], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "3856023d-0393-4f0c-a557-cc43ccdd8b90"],
 " that worked in the second limit was 2\[Delta].\n\nA harder version of \
Problem 7 would be to show that the following two limits (if one exists), \
must be equal, and find the \[Delta] that makes it so.\n\nSo, assume this \
exists:"
}], "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.8284474725875397`*^9, 3.828447589824294*^9}, {
  3.828447670769052*^9, 3.82844769501711*^9}, {3.828447786409136*^9, 
  3.828447884611442*^9}, {3.828447919296382*^9, 3.828447993017722*^9}, {
  3.8284480339297037`*^9, 3.8284480387951593`*^9}, {3.8284481139503307`*^9, 
  3.828448231558095*^9}, {3.8297402766946383`*^9, 3.829740292157325*^9}, {
  3.829740323634078*^9, 3.82974034027992*^9}, {3.829740506812354*^9, 
  3.8297406077798777`*^9}, {3.829740679677334*^9, 
  3.829740687653689*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"4c5c016e-38f8-4166-9b2d-\
85ae79e1c34a"],

Cell[BoxData[
 FormBox[
  RowBox[{"l", "=", 
   TemplateBox[{
     RowBox[{"f", "(", "x", ")"}], "x", "0"},
    "Limit2Arg",
    DisplayFunction->(RowBox[{
       TagBox[
        UnderscriptBox[
         StyleBox["\"lim\"", ShowStringCharacters -> False], 
         RowBox[{#2, "\[Rule]", #3}], LimitsPositioning -> True], Identity, 
        SyntaxForm -> "\[Limit]", Tooltip -> "Limit"], #}]& ),
    InterpretationFunction->(RowBox[{"Limit", "[", 
       RowBox[{#, ",", 
         RowBox[{#2, "->", #3}]}], "]"}]& )]}], TraditionalForm]], "Input",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.828447600501935*^9, 3.828447682234026*^9}, {
  3.8284477752718554`*^9, 3.828447782605606*^9}, {3.828447999643751*^9, 
  3.8284480268688927`*^9}},
 CellLabel->
  "In[128]:=",ExpressionUUID->"f42b1188-17a7-4427-b829-47309bc54e12"],

Cell[TextData[{
 "\nWrite out what it means for the above limit to exist.\n\nFrom that, prove \
that the following limit exists and is also ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox["l", TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "4ac884f9-6b1d-4483-a468-b16095904cfd"],
 ". You will once again be finding a ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   RowBox[{"\[Delta]", "'"}], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "fc2829ff-db29-43a1-95fd-3ca971f48031"],
 " that is related to \[Delta]. If you don\[CloseCurlyQuote]t know what to \
do, maybe construct an interesting example to present instead of a proof?"
}], "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.8284474725875397`*^9, 3.828447589824294*^9}, {
  3.828447670769052*^9, 3.82844769501711*^9}, {3.828447786409136*^9, 
  3.828447884611442*^9}, {3.828447919296382*^9, 3.828447993017722*^9}, {
  3.8284480339297037`*^9, 3.828448063668583*^9}, {3.8297406993202868`*^9, 
  3.8297407028521852`*^9}, {3.829741198454422*^9, 3.829741255547838*^9}, {
  3.8297413639407167`*^9, 
  3.829741507849416*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"e4847b32-4fe2-439f-8b28-\
8d7f8400a934"],

